{"id": 1197, "genre": 1001, "title": "啥样的小区让你感觉有“安全感”？", "description": "是那种，背包开了都不害怕丢东西的安全感。（题图来自：Reps）", "record_count": 4186, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160831174225l7mia3PVQvyUIdMT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-02T17:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 112896, "content": "很多都是朋友，或年轻，或年老，或矜持，或热情", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743321}, {"id": 112897, "content": "20年前那样，家家户户大门常开，邻里间随意串门。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453882}, {"id": 113153, "content": "和G20的杭州一个样的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547590}, {"id": 112898, "content": "像一个四合院一样，大家都住在一块儿，家家户户都友好交往 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744782}, {"id": 113154, "content": "下班回家能听到小朋友玩耍的喧闹声，看到拎着菜篮回家的主妇们", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 577839}, {"id": 112899, "content": "有自己珍惜的和珍惜自己的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120781}, {"id": 113155, "content": "以前经常出门忘了锁门，半夜2点也敢一个人在路上走着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745812}, {"id": 112900, "content": "感觉说的和我们这里差不多", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258096}, {"id": 113156, "content": "与其想这事情，那我建议开发商还是把隔音效果，做好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745814}, {"id": 112901, "content": "小孩单独出小区门会被保安拦下找家长", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602278}, {"id": 113158, "content": "啥都有，小世界的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745840}, {"id": 113160, "content": "邻里街坊关系很好，偶尔能听见各种叫卖声，小区内有各种小吃、杂货摊贩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745818}, {"id": 113161, "content": "是那种每家每户熟到没带钥匙，随便进哪家门都行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743316}, {"id": 113162, "content": "小区里花坛植被树木多。环境空气好。卫生整洁干净。", "image": "img/option/option/20160904172531yUJF4RN5slWkYVmg.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745848}, {"id": 112908, "content": "有围墙 有安保 有摄像头 有24小时的便利店 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737373}, {"id": 113164, "content": "距离主干道近", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4621}, {"id": 112909, "content": "邻居都认识 电梯里逗孩子聊着天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682076}, {"id": 112911, "content": "有保安，安全设备齐全", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744824}, {"id": 112912, "content": "每家每户都认识  幸福感满满的小区", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744828}, {"id": 113170, "content": "返璞归真，安静舒适，森林公园，和谐邻里。周边没有门市，但是却要有便利店（通用我们需要的一切）安全巡逻，交通方便", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736128}, {"id": 112915, "content": "邻里之间友好相处，像一家人一样，遇到困难能互相帮助。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744829}, {"id": 112916, "content": "在部队里面住着，门口有哨兵，楼下有自卫哨，小区里面还有两个巡逻的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741042}, {"id": 152341, "content": "楼下派出所，出门有军队驻扎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898952}, {"id": 113431, "content": "没有老王，呃……没有老宋的小区", "image": "img/option/option/20160905165127ukLiVJ1sNMgXObwR", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747016}, {"id": 112920, "content": "保安认识住户们  陌生人一定不能进啊 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735808}, {"id": 113176, "content": "很晚回家也有路灯照亮小路的那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744171}, {"id": 112921, "content": "关键的地方有监控，保安定时巡逻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744827}, {"id": 112922, "content": "邻居间都认识", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688108}, {"id": 112923, "content": "在家里，有个人正在等你回来的小区。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744863}, {"id": 112925, "content": "电梯里遇见的人都是熟人，可以随意聊天。一栋楼住了谁，门清儿~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744885}, {"id": 112926, "content": "大家互相认识就很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744900}, {"id": 112930, "content": "和邻居，物业，门卫处好关系吧首先", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698777}, {"id": 112933, "content": "出入，保安都能主动要求登记", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737586}, {"id": 113190, "content": "我喜欢住乡下什么都好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668103}, {"id": 112937, "content": "有一个心仪的邻居", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 379178}, {"id": 113193, "content": "邻里和睦，安全防范非常到位，好的甚至可以出门不锁门。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704247}, {"id": 112939, "content": "好友都是邻居的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744948}, {"id": 112940, "content": "安全感是幸福感的一种，有安全感，就有幸福感，反过来，幸福感也促进安全感的产生。所以，我觉得，有宝宝在，就有了最关键的安全感，心里好踏实。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743781}, {"id": 116269, "content": "只有我一个人住的小区。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759459}, {"id": 112942, "content": "我住的这个小区，周围全是退休的老大爷大妈大婶。。我们这种年轻人竟成了异类。。大妈能带给我安全感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727597}, {"id": 112689, "content": "首先，我得是住在一个小区。", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727357}, {"id": 112945, "content": "现在的，7号以前的杭州", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594914}, {"id": 113201, "content": "广告?什么时候下班都有得吃，都有可爱的保安护送的小区～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696587}, {"id": 112690, "content": "G20时西湖边的小区。居民自己都不一定进得去???", "image": null, "praise_count": 221, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714512}, {"id": 112947, "content": "租户少", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740748}, {"id": 112948, "content": "邻里和睦，互爱互助。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740032}, {"id": 112695, "content": "下班回家发现早上门没关好 进屋啥都没掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704402}, {"id": 112696, "content": "摄像头多", "image": null, "praise_count": 138, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 501377}, {"id": 112952, "content": "人都大致认得，特别是门卫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216033}, {"id": 112697, "content": "买东西方便，邻居都认识，都知道邻居是干什么的", "image": null, "praise_count": 166, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253159}]}